<A>__{the main hallway and waiting room of the police station in marrakesh. french and arab personnel move up and down the wide hallway from one doorway to another. there is a babble of voices and the sound of phones heard off. the mckennas and drayton are seated on a long bench, waiting to be called into the inner office of the police inspector. drayton sits next to ben. it is hot. jo has eyes for everything, but ben seems to be somewhat impatient. he looks at his watch for the third or fourth time in a minute.}
